member.example:
This shows how to add lines in ituff header.

var ituffHeaderLine = "MyItuffHeaderDataToBePrintedInLevelSix";
Prime.Services.DatalogService.AddLevelSixItuffHeader(myInstanceName, ituffHeaderLine);

This shows how to set token for saving ituff data for instance 'INSTANCE_A' in module 'TPI_BASE' , whise data in ituff looks like this.
2_tname_TPI_BASE::INSTANCE_A
2_mrslt_0.5A.

var ituffTokens = new HashSet<string>();
ituffTokens.Add("TPI_BASE::INSTANCE_A");
Prime.Services.DatalogService.SetTokensToSaveItuffData(ituffTokens, this.sessionContext);
.
